# The base image build (build_images.py --mode base) uses the repo ROOT as its
# Docker context so the Dockerfile can COPY the vendored MCP (mcps/linux). Only
# base/ and mcps/ are needed there — exclude everything else to keep the context
# small. Leaf builds use their own per-CVE context and are unaffected.
*
!base
!base/**
!mcps
!mcps/**
